To install Bio::PrimerDesigner, run the following commands:

  $ perl Makefile.PL
  $ make
  $ make test
  $ su
  # make install

To learn which arguments Makefile.PL accepts, run the following command:

  $ perl Makefile.PL [-h|--help]


NOTE: For local installations, make sure you have installed te binary executables
for your OS for primer3 and e-PCR

e-PCR: http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sutils/e-pcr/

primer3: http://primer3.sourceforge.net


If you have problems, please contact the author:

  Sheldon McKay <mckays@cshl.edu>


